de.dfki.lt.hfc

Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dfki.lt.hfc.Table

  •  class Table
extends java.lang.Object
    an auxiliary class that hides query/binding tables (sets of tuples: Set) and so-called "delta", subsets of the tables, encoding only the new information from the last iteration step
    Since:
    JDK 1.5
